room_title: Escape room "The Hike" by Escape Again Rooms in Houston
room_description: Hiking through the woods, you didn't even notice the moment when the darkness set in and the rain became heavier. With the forest getting more and more unfamiliar, you eventually realize that you are lost and have no choice but to find shelter. Luckily you stumble upon an abandoned cabin. But when you enter, you don't feel so lucky anymore...
